{"tid":1529921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［粵語］美國國歌普世價值版本","createTime":"2019-09-01T23:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:37:31.000Z","uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d813fa7aecb14af534b65691558cc2fa88d1ab9c","tid":1529921,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:39:45.000Z","msg":"見有巴打將美國國歌譜上粵語歌詞，我又獻下醜，用美國國歌象徵普世價值，寫咗一首詞，中間一段保留英語，以便與美國人共唱，請各位巴絲指教：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世上人人同享<br />\n不分種族信仰<br />\n人權、普選、法治<br />\n免於威逼我自由<br />\n<br />\n不論何地何國<br />\n不管富裕落泊<br />\n和平、公正、信義<br />\n免於饑苦與病寒<br />\n<br />\nAnd the rockets' red glare, the bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there;<br />\n<br />\n無畏刀山火海<br />\n莫怕魔黨試煉<br />\n凡我手足，人人勇武直前"},{"pid":"6ab0921703291a0417184c90e7a54a58e0c7da56","tid":1529921,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"人地個創作背景係1812年戰爭"},{"pid":"4a798efc5d68a85bfbf837149a670edddd3d32ab","tid":1529921,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ab0921703291a0417184c90e7a54a58e0c7da56","tid":1529921,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"人地個創作背景係1812年戰爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"我想賦予新意義，同普世價值連接"},{"pid":"b9226a25d8d2fb48dc24ad2c3415cb03d791cb36","tid":1529921,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a798efc5d68a85bfbf837149a670edddd3d32ab","tid":1529921,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ab0921703291a0417184c90e7a54a58e0c7da56","tid":1529921,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"人地個創作背景係1812年戰爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"我想賦予新意義，同普世價值連接"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:47:23.000Z","msg":"同埋講畀美國人聽，我地追求普世價值，冇人欣賞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e81c4e7a3803fc